---
// Standalone print-only resume page — no shared layout
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Yaroslav Kovalchuk — Resume</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@300;400;500&family=Geist+Mono:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }

    :root {
      --ink:       #30374E;
      --ink-mid:   rgba(48, 55, 78, 0.52);
      --ink-dim:   rgba(48, 55, 78, 0.36);
      --ink-faint: rgba(48, 55, 78, 0.09);
    }

    body {
      width: 210mm;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;
      font-size: 10.5px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    .page {
      padding: 13mm 16mm 12mm;
    }

    .r-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding-bottom: 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-faint);
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .r-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .r-tagline {
      font-size: 9.5px;
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ink-mid);
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .r-contact {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto auto;
      column-gap: 24px;
      row-gap: 4px;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .c-item {
      font-size: 9.5px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--ink-mid);
      text-align: left;
    }

    .c-item a {
      color: var(--ink-mid);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .r-section {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 96px 1fr;
      column-gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .r-section-label {
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.13em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ink-dim);
      padding-top: 13px;
    }

    .r-entries {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .r-entry {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 175px 1fr;
      column-gap: 20px;
      padding: 11px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-faint);
    }

    .r-entries .r-entry:last-child {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-faint);
    }

    .r-company {
      font-size: 10.5px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .r-role {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--ink-mid);
      margin-top: 2px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .r-date {
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 8.5px;
      color: var(--ink-dim);
      margin-top: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .r-desc {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--ink-mid);
      line-height: 1.65;
      padding-top: 1px;
    }

    .r-entry--solo {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .r-flat {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 175px 1fr;
      column-gap: 20px;
      padding: 9px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-faint);
    }

    .r-entries .r-flat:last-child {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-faint);
    }

    .r-flat-cat {
      font-size: 10.5px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--ink);
      padding-top: 1px;
    }

    .r-flat-val {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--ink-mid);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <header class="r-header">
    <div>
      <div class="r-name">Yaroslav Kovalchuk</div>
      <div class="r-tagline">Product Designer</div>
    </div>
    <div class="r-contact">
      <span class="c-item"><a href="https://yaroslav.design">yaroslav.design</a></span>
      <span class="c-item"><a href="mailto:hello@yaroslav.design">hello@yaroslav.design</a></span>
      <span class="c-item"><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yaroslavdesign">linkedin.com/in/yaroslavdesign</a></span>
      <span class="c-item">+380 95 445 6831</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="r-section">
    <div class="r-section-label">Experience</div>
    <div class="r-entries">

      <div class="r-entry">
        <div>
          <div class="r-company">Headway Inc</div>
          <div class="r-role">Product Designer, Growth</div>
          <div class="r-date">Jan 2025 — Present</div>
        </div>
        <div class="r-desc">Web Growth team — conversion funnels, landing pages, and A/B tests. Focused on acquisition and activation metrics for a global EdTech product.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="r-entry">
        <div>
          <div class="r-company">Quidget</div>
          <div class="r-role">Product Designer</div>
          <div class="r-date">Jan 2023 — Jan 2025</div>
        </div>
        <div class="r-desc">Founding designer. Built the entire product from zero — AI chat widget platform, web app, brand identity, and marketing site.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="r-entry">
        <div>
          <div class="r-company">SupportYourApp</div>
          <div class="r-role">UX/UI Designer</div>
          <div class="r-date">Oct 2021 — Jan 2025</div>
        </div>
        <div class="r-desc">Enterprise helpdesk product design. Quidget originated here as an internal tool before spinning out as a standalone company.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="r-entry r-entry--solo">
        <div>
          <div class="r-company">SupportYourApp</div>
          <div class="r-role">Technical Support Specialist</div>
          <div class="r-date">Mar 2019 — Oct 2021</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="r-entry r-entry--solo">
        <div>
          <div class="r-company">99designs</div>
          <div class="r-role">Designer</div>
          <div class="r-date">Aug 2017 — Mar 2019</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="r-entry r-entry--solo">
        <div>
          <div class="r-company">Freelancehunt</div>
          <div class="r-role">Designer</div>
          <div class="r-date">Aug 2016 — Aug 2017</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="r-section">
    <div class="r-section-label">Education</div>
    <div class="r-entries">

      <div class="r-entry r-entry--solo">
        <div>
          <div class="r-company">Projector Institute</div>
          <div class="r-role">Web Design</div>
          <div class="r-date">2021 — 2022</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="r-entry r-entry--solo">
        <div>
          <div class="r-company">Kyiv National University of Culture and Arts</div>
          <div class="r-role">BA, Language Interpretation and Translation</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="r-section">
    <div class="r-section-label">Skills</div>
    <div class="r-entries">

      <div class="r-flat">
        <div class="r-flat-cat">Design</div>
        <div class="r-flat-val">Product Design, UI Design, Growth Design, Figma, Design Systems, Prototyping, A/B Testing</div>
      </div>

      <div class="r-flat">
        <div class="r-flat-cat">Languages</div>
        <div class="r-flat-val">Ukrainian (Native) &nbsp;·&nbsp; English (Full Professional) &nbsp;·&nbsp; Polish (Limited Working)</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
